room_title: Escape room "No Vacancy" by West Palm Beach Escape Rooms in West Palm Beach
room_address: 209 S. Olive Ave West Palm Beach, FL 33401
room_description: Your friends book a stay at a luxury hotel only to find out there was no vacancy when you arrived. After hours of searching, you come across a hotel that’s able to accommodate your guests and as soon as you’re being guided to your room, the bellman smirks and pulls a gun behind his back and states “ escape this room in one hour and I will set you free, If not you won’t be checking out anytime soon.” and proceeds to slam the door shut behind you. You and your team have no idea as to why someone would want to play this sick and twisted game, but do you really have a choice?
